var e=[{id:`L2_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`MIMIC_CORRUPTED_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`친구를 사귀는 건 멍청해. 나만큼 소중한 걸 곁에 두다니. 방해야.`,JPN:`友達を作るなんてバカらしい。自分と同じくらい大切な存在なんて、邪魔なだけだよ。`,ENG:`Making friends is dumb. Keeping something as precious as me nearby is a liability.`,TWN:`交朋友是愚蠢的。把像我這樣珍貴的東西留在身邊，得防著點。`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`MIMIC_CORRUPTED_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_IDLE`},R:null}}},{id:`L3_1`,type:`dialog`,speaker:`MIMIC_CORRUPTED_NULL_NULL`,text:{KOREA:`그래서 네 방식 맘에 들어. 그 비즈니스란 거, 나한테도 유용하거든. 키히히, 앞으로도 우린 함께야.`,JPN:`だからあなたのやり方は好き。ビジネスってやつは私にも役立つから。キヒヒ、これからも一緒だよね？　私たち。`,ENG:`That's why I like your approach. That business thing, it's useful for me as well. Keeheehee, we'll be together from here on out.`,TWN:`我喜歡你的做事方式。那個交易，對我也有用呢。嘻嘻嘻，之後也合作愉快囉。`},stage:{bg:`LIFETIME`,bgm:`CUTSCENE_HOPE`,filter:`NCFT_NORMAL`,slots:{L:null,C:{char_id:`MIMIC_CORRUPTED_NULL_NULL`,face:`UNIT_PRIDE`},R:null}}}];export{e as default};